    "Our TTR indicates that our source text was a highly specialised, complex text from the legal domain.",
    "We controlled text complexity and difficulty to analyse MT output under the constraints of legal wording and terminology.",
    "The chosen text was entered directly into the Google Translate website and the translation output was generated, while the following prompt was used for both of the LLMs in our study: \"Please provide the [Spanish/Catalan/ Turkish/Brazilian Portuguese] translation of the following text: [TEXT]\", as per the recommendations of Jiao et al. (2023).",
    "This is recommended to be the best prompt for instructing LLMs to translate.",
